This paper is primarily focused on distributed optimization methods for training machine learning models, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG). However, the paper also discusses issues related to communication and efficiency, which could potentially fall under the categories of distributed computing (cs.DC), data structures and algorithms (cs.DS), numerical analysis (cs.NA), and control systems (cs.SY).
